      <div class="chat-msg-row chat-msg-row--ai flex justify-start anim-fade-up">
        <div class="chat-msg-col chat-msg-col--ai">
          <div class="message-bubble ai bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-2xl rounded-bl-sm px-4 py-3 shadow-sm">
          <div class="chat-msg-body text-xs text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed"><div class="chat-msg-text">你好！😊 很高兴认识你～ 今天想聊点什么呀？</div></div>
