                <div class="px-3 py-2 text-[10px] text-gray-400 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">🔥 热门聊天模型</div>
                <div class="chat-picker-list py-1 max-h-60 overflow-y-auto">
