        <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium">如何连接到GUID.AI？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon text-gray-400 text-sm transition-transform duration-200">▼</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-body hidden p-3 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed pt-3">
            GUID.AI使用MCP（Model Context Protocol），这是一个开放标准，允许AI代理访问外部工具。
            <br><br>
            连接步骤：<br>
            1. 获取API密钥（在<a href="#" onclick="showPage('api');closeModal('create-key-modal');showToast('📄 跳转API令牌页面')" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">API令牌页面</a>创建）<br>
            2. 将MCP配置添加到你的Agent设置中<br>
            3. 在对话中直接调用GUID.AI的功能
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium">哪些Agent支持？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon text-gray-400 text-sm transition-transform duration-200">▼</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-body hidden p-3 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed pt-3">
            支持以下Agent：
            <br>• Claude Web、Claude Code
            <br>• Cursor IDE
            <br>• Codex
            <br>• OpenClaw Agent
            <br>• Hermes Agent
            <br>• NemoClaw
            <br><br>
            任何支持MCP协议的客户端都可以连接。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium">费用如何计算？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon text-gray-400 text-sm transition-transform duration-200">▼</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-body hidden p-3 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed pt-3">
            Skills功能使用与平台相同的积分系统（⚡算力）：
            <br><br>
            • 图片生成：⚡0.06-0.24/次
            <br>• 视频生成：⚡0.35-2.80/次
            <br>• 对话调用：按token计费
            <br><br>
            你的平台积分余额会自动用于Skills调用。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium">生成需要多长时间？</span>
          <span class="faq-icon text-gray-400 text-sm transition-transform duration-200">▼</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-body hidden p-3 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
          <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed pt-3">
            生成时间取决于模型和复杂度：
            <br><br>
            • 图片生成：通常 5-30 秒
            <br>• 视频生成：通常 1-5 分钟
            <br>• 音频生成：通常 10-60 秒
            <br><br>
            具体时间会受当前负载影响。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
