          <div class="mcp-nav-item px-2 py-1.5 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30" data-section="faq-pricing" onclick="scrollToSection('faq-pricing')">费用如何计算？</div>
          <div class="mcp-nav-item px-2 py-1.5 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30" data-section="faq-key" onclick="scrollToSection('faq-key')">需要API密钥？</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 右侧内容 -->
    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0 space-y-5" id="mcp-docs-content">
      <!-- 简介 -->
      <div id="section-intro" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">📖 简介</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <p>MCP（Model Context Protocol）是一个开放标准，允许AI代理访问外部工具。GUID.AI通过MCP协议，让您的AI Agent具备图像和视频生成能力。</p>
          <div class="p-3 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg text-[11px] space-y-1">
            <div>✅ 支持30+顶尖AI模型</div>
            <div>✅ 图片/视频/音频全能力</div>
            <div>✅ 无需API密钥，账号认证即可</div>
            <div>✅ 与平台积分体系打通</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 安装配置 -->
      <div id="section-setup" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">⚙️ 安装配置</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-3">
          <p>将以下MCP配置添加到你的Agent客户端配置文件中：</p>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto">
            <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">{
  "mcpServers": {
    "guid": {
      "url": "https://api.guid.ai/mcp",
      "headers": {
        "Authorization": "Bearer YOUR_API_KEY"
      }
    }
  }
}</pre>
          </div>
          <button onclick="copyMcpConfig()" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">📋 复制配置</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 第一个请求 -->
      <div id="section-first" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">🚀 第一个请求</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <p>配置完成后，在Agent中直接说：<strong>"用GUID生成一张赛博朋克图片"</strong></p>
          <p>Agent会通过MCP协议调用GUID.AI的图像生成API，返回生成的图片。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 对话API -->
      <div id="section-chat-api" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">💬 对话API</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>端点：</strong><span class="font-mono text-blue-600">https://api.guid.ai/v1/chat/completions</span></div>
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>方法：</strong>POST</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto mt-2">
            <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">curl -X POST https://api.guid.ai/v1/chat/completions \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "model": "GPT-5.4",
    "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "你好"}]
  }'</pre>
          </div>
          <button onclick="copyCode(this, 'curl')" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">📋 复制代码</button>
          <div class="text-[11px] font-medium mt-2">响应示例：</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto">
            <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">{
  "choices": [{
    "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": "你好！有什么我可以帮助你的吗？"}
  }]
}</pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 图像API -->
      <div id="section-image-api" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">🖼️ 图像API</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>端点：</strong><span class="font-mono text-blue-600">https://api.guid.ai/v1/images/generations</span></div>
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>方法：</strong>POST</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto mt-2">
            <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">curl -X POST https://api.guid.ai/v1/images/generations \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "prompt": "赛博朋克城市夜景",
    "model": "Nano Banana Pro",
    "size": "1024x1024"
  }'</pre>
          </div>
          <button onclick="copyCode(this, 'curl')" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">📋 复制代码</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 视频API -->
      <div id="section-video-api" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">🎬 视频API</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>端点：</strong><span class="font-mono text-blue-600">https://api.guid.ai/v1/video/generations</span></div>
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>方法：</strong>POST</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto mt-2">
            <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">curl -X POST https://api.guid.ai/v1/video/generations \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "prompt": "未来城市航拍",
    "model": "VIDU-音乐MV",
    "duration": 15
  }'</pre>
          </div>
          <button onclick="copyCode(this, 'curl')" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">📋 复制代码</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 音频API -->
      <div id="section-audio-api" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">🎵 音频API</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>端点：</strong><span class="font-mono text-blue-600">https://api.guid.ai/v1/audio/generations</span></div>
          <div class="text-[11px]"><strong>方法：</strong>POST</div>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto mt-2">
            <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">curl -X POST https://api.guid.ai/v1/audio/generations \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "prompt": "治愈系纯音乐",
    "model": "海螺音乐生成",
    "duration": 30
  }'</pre>
          </div>
          <button onclick="copyCode(this, 'curl')" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">📋 复制代码</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Python SDK -->
      <div id="section-python-sdk" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">🐍 Python SDK</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto mb-2">
          <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">pip install guid-ai-sdk

from guid_ai import GUIDClient
client = GUIDClient(api_key="YOUR_API_KEY")
response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="GPT-5.4",
    messages=[{"role": "user", "content": "你好"}]
)</pre>
        </div>
        <button onclick="copyCode(this, 'py')" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">📋 复制代码</button>
      </div>

      <!-- JS SDK -->
      <div id="section-js-sdk" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2">📦 JavaScript SDK</div>
        <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 rounded-xl p-3 overflow-x-auto mb-2">
          <pre class="text-[10px] text-green-400 leading-relaxed font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap">npm install guid-ai-sdk

import { GUIDClient } from 'guid-ai-sdk';
const client = new GUIDClient({ apiKey: "YOUR_API_KEY" });
const response = await client.chat.completions.create({
    model: "GPT-5.4",
    messages: [{ role: "user", content: "你好" }]
});</pre>
        </div>
        <button onclick="copyCode(this, 'js')" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">📋 复制代码</button>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div id="section-faq-agents" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-5 scroll-mt-20">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3">❓ 常见问题</div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium">支持哪些Agent？</span><span class="faq-icon text-gray-400 text-sm">▼</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-body hidden p-3 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed pt-3">支持 Claude Web、Claude Code、Cursor IDE、Codex、OpenClaw Agent、Hermes Agent、NemoClaw 等任何支持MCP协议的客户端。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium">费用如何计算？</span><span class="faq-icon text-gray-400 text-sm">▼</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-body hidden p-3 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed pt-3">使用平台积分（⚡算力）计费：图片生成⚡0.06-0.24/次，视频生成⚡0.35-2.80/次，对话按token计费。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="faq-header flex items-center justify-between p-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium">需要API密钥吗？</span><span class="faq-icon text-gray-400 text-sm">▼</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-body hidden p-3 pt-0 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed pt-3">需要在<a href="#" onclick="showPage('api')" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">API令牌页面</a>创建密钥，配置到MCP配置文件中进行身份验证。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

    <section id="page-model-hub" class="page-section">
  <div class="flex gap-0" style="min-height: calc(100vh - 56px);">
    
    <!-- 左侧筛选面板 -->
    <aside id="model-sidebar" class="w-52 shrink-0 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border-r border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 p-4">
      <!-- 筛选标题 -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">筛选</span>
        <button onclick="resetModelFilters()" class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-500 transition">重置</button>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 供应商 -->
      <div class="mb-5">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">供应商</div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          <span class="model-filter-chip active px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border" data-filter="provider" data-value="all" style="color:#7C3AED;border-color:#7C3AED;background:rgba(124,58,237,0.08);">全部供应商</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="provider" data-value="Google"><span class="mr-0.5 text-blue-400">◆</span>Google</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="provider" data-value="OpenAI"><span class="mr-0.5 text-green-400">◎</span>OpenAI</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="provider" data-value="阿里巴巴"><span class="mr-0.5 text-orange-400">✧</span>阿里巴巴</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 可用令牌分组 -->
      <div class="mb-5">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">可用令牌分组</div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          <span class="model-filter-chip active px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border" data-filter="group" data-value="all" style="color:#7C3AED;border-color:#7C3AED;background:rgba(124,58,237,0.08);">全部分组</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="group" data-value="default">default</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="group" data-value="vip">vip</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 计费类型 -->
      <div class="mb-5">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">计费类型</div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          <span class="model-filter-chip active px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border" data-filter="billing" data-value="all" style="color:#7C3AED;border-color:#7C3AED;background:rgba(124,58,237,0.08);">全部类型</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="billing" data-value="按量计费">按量计费</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="billing" data-value="按次计费">按次计费</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 标签 -->
      <div class="mb-5">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">标签</div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          <span class="model-filter-chip active px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border" data-filter="tag" data-value="all" style="color:#7C3AED;border-color:#7C3AED;background:rgba(124,58,237,0.08);">全部标签</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 端点类型 -->
      <div class="mb-5">
        <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">端点类型</div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          <span class="model-filter-chip active px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border" data-filter="endpoint" data-value="all" style="color:#7C3AED;border-color:#7C3AED;background:rgba(124,58,237,0.08);">全部端点</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="endpoint" data-value="gemini">gemini</span>
          <span class="model-filter-chip px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:border-gray-300 dark:hover:border-gray-500" data-filter="endpoint" data-value="openai">openai</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
    
    <!-- 右侧主内容区 -->
    <div class="flex-1 p-4">
      <!-- 蓝色横幅区域 -->
      <div class="relative rounded-xl p-5 mb-4 overflow-hidden" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3B82F6 0%,#2563EB 50%,#1E40AF 100%);">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-white">全部供应商</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-white/20 rounded-full text-[10px] text-white font-medium">共 <span id="model-count-badge">33</span> 个模型</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/80">查看所有可用的AI模型供应商，包括众多知名供应商的模型。</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 右侧装饰 -->
        <div class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-10">
          <svg width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="white">
            <path d="M40 0C17.9 0 0 17.9 0 40s17.9 40 40 40 40-17.9 40-40S62.1 0 40 0zm0 70c-16.5 0-30-13.5-30-30S23.5 10 40 10s30 13.5 30 30-13.5 30-30 30z"/>
            <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="15"/>
            <path d="M40 20L45 35L60 35L48 45L53 60L40 50L27 60L32 45L20 35L35 35Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 搜索工具栏 -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 flex-wrap">
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-[200px] flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">🔍</span>
          <input id="model-search-input" class="flex-1 text-xs border-0 outline-none bg-transparent text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 placeholder-gray-400" placeholder="模糊搜索模型名称" oninput="clearSelectedModels(); filterModelCards(); updateCopyButton()">
        </div>
        <button id="copy-btn" onclick="copyModels()" class="flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-2 text-[11px] border rounded-lg transition text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 cursor-not-allowed">
          <span>📋</span><span>复制</span>
        </button>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">充值价格显示</span>
          <div class="toggle-switch w-8 h-4 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full relative cursor-pointer" onclick="togglePriceDisplay(this)">
            <div class="knob w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full absolute top-0.5 left-0.5 transition-all"></div>
          </div>
          <!-- 货币选择下拉框 -->
          <select id="currency-select" class="hidden text-[11px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-2 py-1 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 outline-none cursor-pointer" onchange="onCurrencyChange(this.value)">
            <option value="USD">USD</option>
            <option value="CNY" selected>CNY</option>
            <option value="custom">自定义货币</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">倍率</span>
          <div class="toggle-switch w-8 h-4 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-full relative cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleRateDisplay(this)">
            <div class="knob w-3 h-3 bg-white rounded-full absolute top-0.5 left-0.5 transition-all"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 表格视图切换按钮 -->
        <button id="view-toggle-btn" onclick="toggleModelView()" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 text-[11px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <span>表格视图</span>
        </button>
        <button id="unit-toggle-btn" onclick="togglePriceUnit()" class="px-2 py-2 text-[11px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 font-bold text-blue-500">M</button>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 模型卡片网格 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3" id="model-card-grid-new">
        <!-- 由 JS 动态渲染 -->
      </div>
      
      <!-- 模型列表视图 -->
      <div class="hidden" id="model-list-view-new">
        <!-- 由 JS 动态渲染 -->
      </div>
      
      <!-- 分页 -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
          <button onclick="modelPagePrev()" class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 text-xs">＜</button>
          <button class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-500 text-white text-xs font-medium">1</button>
          <button onclick="modelPageNext()" class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 text-xs">＞</button>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">每页条数：</span>
          <select class="text-[11px] border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-lg px-2 py-1 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 outline-none">
            <option>20</option>
            <option>50</option>
            <option>100</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

