          <span class="channel-strategy-btn px-3 py-1.5 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition" data-strategy="speed" onclick="selectStrategy(this)">速度优先</span>
          <span class="channel-strategy-btn px-3 py-1.5 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition" data-strategy="success" onclick="selectStrategy(this)">成功率优先</span>
          <span class="channel-strategy-btn px-3 py-1.5 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-[10px] rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition" data-strategy="custom" onclick="selectStrategy(this)">自定义</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">
          💡 价格优先：优先使用价格最低的渠道<br>
          速度优先：优先使用响应最快的渠道<br>
          成功率优先：优先使用最稳定的渠道<br>
          自定义：按勾选的渠道列表顺序调用
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 分隔线 -->
      <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700"></div>

      <!-- 调用限额 -->
      <div>
        <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500 mb-2">调用限额</div>
        <div class="relative limit-select-wrapper" style="max-width:200px">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 cursor-pointer limit-select-trigger" onclick="toggleLimitDropdown(event)">
            <span class="limit-select-text">0 = 不限</span>
            <span class="text-gray-400 text-[10px]">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="limit-dropdown hidden absolute left-0 top-full mt-1 w-full bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl shadow-lg z-50">
            <div class="p-1">
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs" data-limit="0">0 = 不限</div>
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs" data-limit="100">100 次/日</div>
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs" data-limit="500">500 次/日</div>
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs" data-limit="1000">1,000 次/日</div>
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs" data-limit="5000">5,000 次/日</div>
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs" data-limit="10000">10,000 次/日</div>
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs" data-limit="50000">50,000 次/日</div>
              <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 my-1"></div>
              <div class="limit-option px-3 py-2 hover:bg-blue-50 dark:hover:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer text-xs text-blue-500" data-limit="custom">自定义...</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mt-1">💡 设置每日调用限额，防止超额消费。0表示不限。</div>
      </div>

      <!-- 分隔线 -->
      <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700"></div>

      <!-- 警告 -->
      <div class="flex items-start gap-2 p-3 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 border border-red-200 dark:border-red-800 rounded-lg">
        <span class="text-red-500 text-sm">⚠️</span>
        <span class="text-[11px] text-red-700 dark:text-red-300">请妥善保管密钥，它等同于您的账号密码。创建后请立即保存。</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 底部按钮 -->
    <div class="flex justify-end gap-2 mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
      <button onclick="closeModal('create-key-modal')" class="px-5 py-2 text-xs border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition">取消</button>
      <button class="confirm-create-key px-5 py-2 text-xs bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition" onclick="confirmCreateKey()">确认创建</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

